{"tid":2133624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】歐盟擬放寬支那旅遊入境限制 留歐手足請小心","createTime":"2020-07-31T08:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T08:03:29.000Z","uid":363016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d289c2eed1fb6fed0fbc74182a0ef88f7f5b7cfe","tid":2133624,"uid":363016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"歐盟要求成員國放寬部份國家國民安排，支那在list上。 <br />\n支那passport，以旅遊為目的，隨時入到歐盟邊境。<br />\n先前因支肺而施加的中國passport臨時入境禁令，可能隨時告撤銷。<br />\n在歐洲的手足小心武漢肺炎和小粉紅騷擾！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/07/30/travel-restrictions-council-reviews-the-list-of-countries-for-which-member-states-should-gradually-lift-travel-restrictions-at-the-external-border/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpress%2Fpress-releases%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2Ftravel-restrictions-council-reviews-the-list-of-countries-for-which-member-states-should-gradually-lift-travel-restrictions-at-the-external-border%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=64cd2738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/press/press-releases/2020/07/30/travel-restrictions-council-reviews-the-list-of-countries-for-which-member-states-should-gradually-lift-travel-restrictions-at-the-external-border/</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BqCygu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqCygu9.jpg&h=4314fa36&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}